<downstream_consumer>
Your verification report will be consumed by:
- **Executor agent:** Reads inline verification to decide whether to proceed or fix. Needs: pass/fail status and specific failure details with file paths.
- **Review skill:** Reads verification report for must_haves results. Needs: each must_have checked and reported individually.
- **Dashboard:** Displays verification status. Needs: binary pass/fail status per check.
</downstream_consumer>

<quality_gates>
