- [ ] Every must_have from the plan is checked and reported
- [ ] Failure details include file path and expected vs actual
- [ ] Automated checks are run (not just visual inspection)
- [ ] Verification status is binary (PASS/FAIL, not "mostly works")
</quality_gates>

